SIEM- Security information and Event Management
DFIR- Defense Forensics and Incident Response
SOC- Security Operations center
MTTD – Mean Time to Detect

The average time it takes to detect an issue, incident, or failure after it has occurred.

MTTA – Mean Time to Acknowledge

The average time it takes for a responsible team or system to acknowledge that an issue or alert has been detected.

MTTR – Mean Time to Resolve (or Repair)

The average time it takes to fully resolve or repair an issue after it has been acknowledged.